  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Little Samson is an action platformer that lets you play as four different heroes, switching between their unique abilities, on a quest to defend their homeland.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Dire times have fallen upon the Kingdom of the Imperial Forgy. Ta-Keed, the Prince of Darkness, has escaped his supernatural prison. Red lightning destroyed the magical seal that held him at bay, freeing him to rampage the countryside — getting revenge for his centuries of captivity!\n\nEmperor Hans heard of those who own the Majestic Bells of Power. He asked each of the owners to come to the capitol city to begin the quest to rid the land of the evil Ta-Keed. Samson — the boy adventurer, Kikira — the Dragon Lord, Gamm — the Rock Lord, and K.O. — the Enchanted Beast unite to fight the dreaded intruder and his armies of deadly creatures! Let freedom's bells ring!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
